headline: Regions Bank Reduces its Prime Lending Rate
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., September 17, 2025--Regions Bank announced it is reducing its prime lending rate to 7.25% effective Sept. 18, 2025.

headline: Regions Financial to Announce Third Quarter 2025 Financial Results on Oct. 17, 2025
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., September 17, 2025--Regions Financial Corp. confirmed its third quarter 2025 financial results will be released on Friday, Oct. 17, 2025.
